{"tid":882433,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實冇人想做人地第三者......","createTime":"2018-10-30T06:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:35:44.000Z","uid":218922,"like":19,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8668b20b88171c78dee1875e9813cf3ae91e0e","tid":882433,"uid":218922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"我知道做人哋第三者係好犯賤<br />\n但係我真係好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁可以點.....<br />\n我就連發夢都成日夢到佢會正正式式拖住我<br />\n同曬佢所有朋友兄弟介紹我先係佢女朋友<br />\n<br />\n係....我真係好愛你....但你已經有一個穩定交往咗好耐嘅女朋友....我唔想再同你偷偷摸摸出街........唔想再做第三者.....因為真係好難受<br />\n<br />\n我比你掂我....係因為我真係好愛你.....我想滿足你...<br />\n如果你只係當我係肉便器，或者當我係隻雞<br />\n係因為你根本就唔明白我有幾愛你！<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該你唔好再搵我</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你每一次搵返我都好似比緊一個假希望我咁</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我以後以後都唔會再同你扯上任何關係</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做人第三者慘過做狗.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">究竟我要點先可以忘記依個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"618b6bdbf1e9421527f23a313e811e7c714dd0b8","tid":882433,"uid":196682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"做狗好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a66f1e625c7ecc2bb4a995a5a94f97fdece301","tid":882433,"uid":74622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"遇到個比佢更好<br />\n佢有女朋友都肯同你出街<br />\n好極有限"},{"pid":"b9b24a44b297a7868a5840c166dce15e3982d3a1","tid":882433,"uid":213460,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:39:2